Class VideoRecording

java.lang.Object
  rain.Product
      rain.VideoRecording
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class VideoRecording
extends Product

This class represents a VideoRecording. It is a specialized version of the Recording class and adds the following data members: director, actors, rating, yearReleased.
